OL,3,CThe Budget: ITV News answers your
OL,4,Cquestions
OL,6,FThe Chancellor announced Labour's
OL,7,Ffirst Budget in 14 years on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fand made big announcements around tax
OL,9,Fhikes and spending cuts. But what does
OL,10,Fit mean for you? Here, ITV News
OL,11,FConsumer Editor Chris Choi answers
OL,12,Fyour questions.
OL,14,FEmployer national insurance
OL,15,Fcontributions
OL,17,FAnnabel Thomas MacGregor is the CEO of
OL,18,Fan independent nursery, which employs
OL,19,Faround 100 people at any one time.
