OL,6,FAs Annabel says, there are big
OL,7,Fconcerns from businesses and charities
OL,8,Fabout the increase in overheads.
OL,10,FThe Chancellor said she will protect
OL,11,Fsmall firms with an allowance of up to
OL,12,F#10,500. To qualify for that allowance
OL,13,Fto reduce employers' NI, firms need to
OL,14,Fbe liable to pay less than #100,000 a
OL,15,Fyear, and Annabel doesn't qualify.
OL,17,FThe government says it will channel
OL,18,Fmoney from VAT on private schools into
OL,19,Fthe childcare sector. As in most
OL,20,Fcases, the Chancellor giveth and the
OL,21,Fchancellor taketh away."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
