OL,6,FAlcohol Duty rates on draught beer,
OL,7,Fcider and wines are going down by
OL,8,F1.7%. Today it's been estimated that
OL,9,Fcould save a typical draught drinker
OL,10,Fup to #57 a year. But there will also
OL,11,Fbe a rise in duty on non-draught
OL,12,Falcohol matching inflation - so maybe
OL,13,Fhold off planning a bender in
OL,14,Fcelebration.
