OL,6,FRob Pearson asked what the Budget
OL,7,Fmeant for inheritance tax,
OL,8,Fparticularly for single people.
OL,10,FInheritance tax thresholds will be
OL,11,Fextended for two more years, until
OL,12,F2030.
OL,14,FThis means the first #325,000 of any
OL,15,Festate can still be inherited tax-free
OL,16,Funtil then. After this, it will still
OL,17,Fbe taxed at 40%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
