OL,6,FThe headline for hospitality is that
OL,7,Fthe sector will get 40% relief on
OL,8,Fbusiness rates in 2025-26 up to a cap
OL,9,Fof #110,000 per business.
OL,11,FThe sector, along with other retail
OL,12,Foutlets, have had business rates
OL,13,Frelief since 2020 at 75% but that had
OL,14,Fbeen due to end in April 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
