OL,6,FShe asked what the government is going
OL,7,Fto do to help with childcare costs -
OL,8,Fincluding the price of driving her
OL,9,Fkids around.
OL,11,FAs a mum of three - including a new
OL,12,Fbaby - part of the job description is
OL,13,Fof course being a free taxi driver.
OL,15,FAmong all the pre-Budget leaks, hints
OL,16,Fand rumours, there were fears of a
OL,17,Frise in fuel duty.
OL,19,FFuel duty hasn't gone up since 2011
OL,20,Fand in March 2022 the last government
OL,21,Freduced it by 5p.
