OL,6,FThe current fuel duty freeze and
OL,7,Ftemporary 5p-a-litre cut will be
OL,8,Fmaintained for a further year.
OL,10,FThis is where Rachel Reeves aimed to
OL,11,Fbe a cheery chancellor, but there have
OL,12,Fbeen lots of questions about whether
OL,13,Fretailers are actually passing that on
OL,14,Fto drivers, with competition officials
OL,15,Fsuggesting we've been overcharged #1.6
OL,16,Fbillion a year at the pumps.
OL,18,FThe scrutiny on how garages justify
