OL,6,FCatherine Warrilow is a mother of two
OL,7,Fwho was made redundant last year. She
OL,8,Fnow owns a small brand consultancy
OL,9,Fwithin the travel sector, and wants to
OL,10,Fknow how the Budget will impact the
OL,11,Fprice of travel.
OL,13,F"I own an electric car but as a family
OL,14,Fwe use buses and trains a lot to get
OL,15,Faround. Because I also work in the
OL,16,Ftravel industry, I'm really interested
OL,17,Fin how it will affect me and my family
OL,18,Fin getting out and about, but also
OL,19,Fother people within the tourism
OL,20,Fsector?"
