OL,6,FThere was a burst of announcements on
OL,7,Fpublic transport, including tunnelling
OL,8,Fwork to bring the HS2 line into Euston
OL,9,Fand upgrades to the TransPennine route.
OL,11,FTrain fares have gone up around 5%
OL,12,Fthis year.
OL,14,FThe government plans to re-nationalise
OL,15,Fwithin five years - nobody seems at
OL,16,Fall certain what impact that will have
OL,17,Fon fares.
OL,19,FThe price cap on single bus tickets in
OL,20,FEngland continues, but gets raised
OL,21,Ffrom #2 to #3.
